{
  "stem": "24111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this way, my mother and I, we got a shelter in Opatovina, [NON-ENGLISH], that is Opatovina Street in the upper part of Zagreb, with an older Jewish couple.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, we had no difficulties in speaking with them because they spoke German.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This part of Yugoslavia's Zagreb, and even Belgrade, was Austrian territory before the First World War.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the First World War started in Sarajevo, if you remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, those old people, they went to Austrian schools, and German [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was their language at that time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Perhaps not the first language, but their second language.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had no difficulty in speaking with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, also, Rosner spoke [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, for example, the taxi driver, we couldn't converse with him because we couldn't understand him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What section of Yugoslavia?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What province was this Zagreb?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was this Slovenia?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maribor is Slovenia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's located in Slovenia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zagreb is located in Croatia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on we found out that the biggest anti-Semites in Yugoslavia are the Ustase, in Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] If I could back up one moment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mentioned Otto Perl, a cousin of mine, came back from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his parents bought him the ticket to go to England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was interned in England, on the Isle of Man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But his parents didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was still in Vienna when my Aunt Marta Perl committed suicide with gas in their kitchen, on the day she got the notification of her being picked up for the Poland transport.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the next day, when the truck arrived to pick them up, my uncle, Paul Perl, Otto's father, had a heart attack and died [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at the moment when he had to enter the truck.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
